---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Week 4: 力の合成と分解">
  <h1>Week 4: 力の合成と分解</h1>
  <p class="subtitle">力を合わせて、力を分けよう！</p>

  <h2>🎯 今日の目標</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>力を合成できる（合力を求める）</li>
    <li>力を分解できる（分力を求める）</li>
    <li>sin・cos を使った計算ができる</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>力はベクトル！</h2>
  
  <div class="highlight-box">
    力には <strong>大きさ</strong> と <strong>向き</strong> がある → 矢印（ベクトル）で表す
  </div>

  <h2>力の合成（合力）</h2>

  <h3>一直線上の力</h3>
  <div class="example">
    <p><strong>同じ向き：</strong>足し算！ 3 N + 4 N = <strong>7 N</strong></p>
    <p><strong>逆向き：</strong>引き算！ 5 N - 2 N = <strong>3 N</strong>（大きい方の向き）</p>
  </div>

  <h3>斜めの力：平行四辺形の法則</h3>
  <div class="highlight-box">
    2つの力を <strong>隣り合う2辺</strong> とする平行四辺形を描く<br/>
    → <strong>対角線</strong> が合力！
  </div>

  <div class="animation-container" id="vector-animation">
    <p style="color: var(--text-secondary);">🎮 ベクトル合成シミュレーター</p>
    <canvas id="vectorCanvas" width="400" height="300"></canvas>
    <p style="font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--text-secondary);">
      赤と青の矢印の先端をドラッグして動かしてみよう！
    </p>
  </div>

  <h3>合力の大きさ（直角の場合）</h3>
  <div class="formula-box">
    <span class="big-formula">|F| = √(Fx² + Fy²)</span>
    <p>三平方の定理（ピタゴラス）を使う！</p>
  </div>

  <div class="example">
    <h4>例：直角に働く2つの力</h4>
    <p>Fx = 3 N（横）、Fy = 4 N（縦）の合力は？</p>
    <p class="formula">|F| = √(3² + 4²) = √(9 + 16) = √25 = <strong>5 N</strong></p>
  </div>

  <h2>力の分解（分力）</h2>

  <div class="highlight-box">
    1つの力を、2つの方向（縦と横）に分ける！
  </div>

  <h3>斜めの力の分解</h3>
  <div class="formula-box">
    <span class="big-formula">Fx = F cos θ</span>
    <span class="big-formula">Fy = F sin θ</span>
  </div>

  <div class="example">
    <h4>💡 sin・cos の覚え方</h4>
    <p><strong>cos（コサイン）</strong>→ 地面に落ちた影（横方向）</p>
    <p><strong>sin（サイン）</strong>→ 壁に映った影（縦方向）</p>
    <img src="" alt="" style="display:none" />
  </div>

  <h3>三角関数の値（暗記！）</h3>
  <table>
    <tr><th>角度</th><th>sin</th><th>cos</th></tr>
    <tr><td>30°</td><td>1/2 = 0.5</td><td>√3/2 ≈ 0.87</td></tr>
    <tr><td>45°</td><td>√2/2 ≈ 0.71</td><td>√2/2 ≈ 0.71</td></tr>
    <tr><td>60°</td><td>√3/2 ≈ 0.87</td><td>1/2 = 0.5</td></tr>
  </table>

  <h2>斜面上の物体</h2>

  <div class="highlight-box">
    重力 mg を斜面に沿って分解すると...
  </div>

  <table>
    <tr><th>成分</th><th>公式</th><th>意味</th></tr>
    <tr><td>斜面に平行（滑り落ちる力）</td><td><strong>mg sin θ</strong></td><td>物体を滑らせる</td></tr>
    <tr><td>斜面に垂直（押し付ける力）</td><td><strong>mg cos θ</strong></td><td>面を押す力</td></tr>
  </table>

  <div class="example">
    <h4>例：30°の斜面</h4>
    <p>質量 2 kg の物体（g = 10 m/s²）</p>
    <p>滑り落ちる力 = 2 × 10 × sin30° = 20 × 0.5 = <strong>10 N</strong></p>
    <p>面を押す力 = 2 × 10 × cos30° = 20 × 0.87 ≈ <strong>17.3 N</strong></p>
  </div>

  <h2>力のつり合い</h2>

  <div class="formula-box">
    <span class="big-formula">ΣFx = 0, ΣFy = 0</span>
    <p>静止している物体は、力がつり合っている！</p>
  </div>

  <h2>練習問題</h2>
  <table>
    <tr><th>問題</th><th>解答</th></tr>
    <tr>
      <td>① F1 = (3, 0) N と F2 = (0, 4) N の合力の大きさは？</td>
      <td><details><summary>答え</summary>5 N（3-4-5の直角三角形）</details></td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td>② 大きさ 10 N、x軸と60°の力の x成分は？</td>
      <td><details><summary>答え</summary>10 × cos60° = 10 × 0.5 = 5 N</details></td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td>③ 45°斜面で質量 4 kg の物体を滑らせる力は？</td>
      <td><details><summary>答え</summary>4 × 10 × sin45° ≈ 28.3 N</details></td>
    </tr>
  </table>

  <h2>📝 今日のポイント</h2>
  <div class="highlight-box">
    <ul>
      <li>✓ 合力：<strong>平行四辺形の対角線</strong></li>
      <li>✓ 分力：<strong>Fx = F cos θ, Fy = F sin θ</strong></li>
      <li>✓ 斜面：滑る力 = <strong>mg sin θ</strong></li>
      <li>✓ つり合い：ΣFx = 0, ΣFy = 0</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div class="nav-buttons">
    <a href="/physics-basic/weeks/week03/" class="nav-btn secondary">← Week 3</a>
    <a href="/physics-basic/weeks/week05/" class="nav-btn">Week 5 へ →</a>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .subtitle {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    margin-top: -0.5rem;
  }
  .formula-box {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #eff6ff, #dbeafe);
    border: 2px solid var(--primary);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    text-align: center;
    margin: 1.5rem 0;
  }
  .big-formula {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: bold;
    color: var(--primary-dark);
    display: block;
    margin: 0.5rem 0;
  }
  .formula {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
    background: #f1f5f9;
    border-radius: 4px;
    font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
  }
  #vectorCanvas {
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 8px;
    background: white;
    cursor: crosshair;
  }
  details summary {
    color: var(--primary);
    font-weight: 600;
    cursor: pointer;
  }
</style>

<script>
  // Simple vector animation
  const canvas = document.getElementById('vectorCanvas') as HTMLCanvasElement;
  if (canvas) {
    const ctx = canvas.getContext('2d');
    const origin = { x: 200, y: 200 };
    let vecA = { x: 80, y: -60 };
    let vecB = { x: 100, y: 40 };
    let dragging: string | null = null;

    function draw() {
      if (!ctx) return;
      ctx.clearRect(0, 0, canvas.width, canvas.height);
      
      // Grid
      ctx.strokeStyle = '#e2e8f0';
      ctx.lineWidth = 1;
      for (let i = 0; i < canvas.width; i += 20) {
        ctx.beginPath();
        ctx.moveTo(i, 0);
        ctx.lineTo(i, canvas.height);
        ctx.stroke();
      }
      for (let i = 0; i < canvas.height; i += 20) {
        ctx.beginPath();
        ctx.moveTo(0, i);
        ctx.lineTo(canvas.width, i);
        ctx.stroke();
      }

      // Parallelogram (dotted)
      ctx.strokeStyle = '#94a3b8';
      ctx.setLineDash([5, 5]);
      ctx.beginPath();
      ctx.moveTo(origin.x + vecA.x, origin.y + vecA.y);
      ctx.lineTo(origin.x + vecA.x + vecB.x, origin.y + vecA.y + vecB.y);
      ctx.lineTo(origin.x + vecB.x, origin.y + vecB.y);
      ctx.stroke();
      ctx.setLineDash([]);

      // Vector A (red)
      drawArrow(ctx, origin.x, origin.y, origin.x + vecA.x, origin.y + vecA.y, '#ef4444', 3);
      
      // Vector B (blue)
      drawArrow(ctx, origin.x, origin.y, origin.x + vecB.x, origin.y + vecB.y, '#3b82f6', 3);
      
      // Resultant (green, thick)
      const resultX = vecA.x + vecB.x;
      const resultY = vecA.y + vecB.y;
      drawArrow(ctx, origin.x, origin.y, origin.x + resultX, origin.y + resultY, '#22c55e', 4);

      // Labels
      ctx.font = 'bold 14px sans-serif';
      ctx.fillStyle = '#ef4444';
      ctx.fillText('A', origin.x + vecA.x + 5, origin.y + vecA.y);
      ctx.fillStyle = '#3b82f6';
      ctx.fillText('B', origin.x + vecB.x + 5, origin.y + vecB.y);
      ctx.fillStyle = '#22c55e';
      ctx.fillText('合力', origin.x + resultX + 5, origin.y + resultY);

      // Magnitude display
      const mag = Math.sqrt(resultX * resultX + resultY * resultY).toFixed(1);
      ctx.fillStyle = '#1e293b';
      ctx.fillText(`|合力| = ${mag}`, 10, 20);
    }

    function drawArrow(ctx: CanvasRenderingContext2D, x1: number, y1: number, x2: number, y2: number, color: string, width: number) {
      const headLen = 12;
      const angle = Math.atan2(y2 - y1, x2 - x1);
      
      ctx.strokeStyle = color;
      ctx.fillStyle = color;
      ctx.lineWidth = width;
      
      ctx.beginPath();
      ctx.moveTo(x1, y1);
      ctx.lineTo(x2, y2);
      ctx.stroke();
      
      ctx.beginPath();
      ctx.moveTo(x2, y2);
      ctx.lineTo(x2 - headLen * Math.cos(angle - Math.PI / 6), y2 - headLen * Math.sin(angle - Math.PI / 6));
      ctx.lineTo(x2 - headLen * Math.cos(angle + Math.PI / 6), y2 - headLen * Math.sin(angle + Math.PI / 6));
      ctx.closePath();
      ctx.fill();
    }

    canvas.addEventListener('mousedown', (e) => {
      const rect = canvas.getBoundingClientRect();
      const x = e.clientX - rect.left;
      const y = e.clientY - rect.top;
      
      const distA = Math.hypot(x - (origin.x + vecA.x), y - (origin.y + vecA.y));
      const distB = Math.hypot(x - (origin.x + vecB.x), y - (origin.y + vecB.y));
      
      if (distA < 20) dragging = 'A';
      else if (distB < 20) dragging = 'B';
    });

    canvas.addEventListener('mousemove', (e) => {
      if (!dragging) return;
      const rect = canvas.getBoundingClientRect();
      const x = e.clientX - rect.left;
      const y = e.clientY - rect.top;
      
      if (dragging === 'A') {
        vecA = { x: x - origin.x, y: y - origin.y };
      } else if (dragging === 'B') {
        vecB = { x: x - origin.x, y: y - origin.y };
      }
      draw();
    });

    canvas.addEventListener('mouseup', () => { dragging = null; });
    canvas.addEventListener('mouseleave', () => { dragging = null; });

    draw();
  }
</script>
